# TradingFlow Shared Schema Rules

- Treat `packages/common` as source of truth for request/response shapes.
- When schema changes, update both backend handlers and client API payload/types in the same task.
- Keep enums and string literals consistent across schema, DB model usage, and client rendering.
- Avoid breaking changes without updating all call sites.
